    • bookSeats

      public static void bookSeats(Session session, String[] seats)
      Books the given array of seats for the given session. If the string input is not a valid seat selection or that the seat selection is already booked, no seat will be booked. Stores the booked seats in a list and passes it to TicketsPayment.
      Parameters:
      session -
      seats -

    • updateCinema

      public static boolean updateCinema(Session session, String cinemaString)
      This method is called when user requests to change the cinema for a session. First search for a cinema matching the given string. If a cinema is found, update the given session with the new cinema.
      Parameters:
      session -

      Returns:
